                    <span>It is truly inspirational to read about a businessman succeeding by being perfectly moral.  Ray Kroc continuously focused on delivering positives instead of negatives.  He was way ahead of his time, realizing the power of the entrepreneurial spirit and how to harness that in a large corporation.</span>
                  
              
